title: All Employees: Financial Activities in FRB-St. Louis District States (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
This series is calculated by FRB-St. Louis using data series from the Bureau of Labor Statistics. FRB-St. Louis District States include Arkansas, Illinois, Indiana, Kentucky, Mississippi, Missouri and Tennessee.

Industry based on 2002 North American Industry Classification System (NAICS). Please consult the U.S. Census Bureau (http://www.census.gov/cgi-bin/sssd/naics/naicsrch?chart=2002) for additional information about NAICS.
